<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-26-0096 </DOCNO><TEXT>Renewable energy sources are discussed with many illustrations, startingwith detailed information an energy conservation (energy balance, energy-savingdesign of buildings, cogeneration). Active and passive solar systemsare mentioned (collections, thermal power plant, hydrogen conversion,roof collectors, solar cells) as well as wind power systems (wind properties,wind pump, windmill) and hydroelectric power generation (rivers, tidalenergy, waves). Each chapter lists books for further reading, interestgroups, and supplies of systems. (HWJ) With 158 figs.</TEXT></DOC>